{"title":"坝上草原远眺","authors":["段和平"],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":9,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"坝上草原远眺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"段和平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿，酣畅的绿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在汇聚，在拥挤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浓绿中，站起一束束异彩纷呈的小花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正接受太阳金色的洗礼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝天没有疆界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白云浮在天际，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深吸一口这草原清甜的空气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命象骤然变得神奇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"剽悍的骏马正踏起尘烟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛群在清澈的泡子里嬉戏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大片大片雪白的羊群，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象绿丝绒上缀满了珠玑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以碧绿作封面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云朵为小序，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以豪壮的畜群作鲜活的诗句，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以各色小花作玲珑的标点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要编一部这样的诗集……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}